<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= home.housename %> | Home Details</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #051022;
      color: #0273d6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: rgb(44, 2, 83);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .home-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 450px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .details {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .details h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .info-grid p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .description {
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .btns {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .btns a, .btns button {
      padding: 12px 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btns a {
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }

    .btns a:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }

    .btns button {
      background-color: #2ecc71;
      color: white;
    }

    .btns button:hover {
      background-color: #27ae60;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://picsum.photos/1000/450" alt="Home Image" class="home-image">

    <div class="details">
      <h1><%= home.housename %></h1>

      <div class="info-grid">
        <p><strong>Owned by:</strong> <%= home.ownedby %></p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= home.location %></p>
        <p><strong>Price per night:</strong> ₹<%= home.price %></p>
        <p><strong>Rating:</strong> ⭐ <%= home.rating %> / 5</p>
      </div>

      <div class="description">
        <p>Welcome to <strong><%= home.housename %></strong>, your perfect getaway destination! Nestled in the heart of <%= home.location %>, this stunning property combines modern design with a cozy ambiance to make you feel right at home.</p>

        <p>Enjoy peaceful mornings on the private balcony, relax in spacious and beautifully decorated rooms, and take advantage of all the premium amenities including high-speed Wi-Fi, a fully equipped kitchen, and 24/7 support. Whether you’re traveling solo, as a couple, or with family, this space is tailored for comfort and convenience.</p>

        <p>Book now to experience unforgettable stays, top-rated service, and a home you'll want to return to again and again.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="btns">
        <a href="/">← Back to Listings</a>
        <button>Book Now</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%-include('partials/footer')%>

</body>
</html>
